  "tree": {
    "id": "root",
    "text": "The Ugly Duckling",
    "emoji": "🦆",
    "state": "emoji",
    "children": [
      {
        "id": "p1",
        "text": "Once upon a time, there was a mother duck. She had six little ducklings.",
        "emoji": "🦆",
        "highlight": "Once upon a time",
        "keywords": "mother duck, six ducklings",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p1_1",
            "text": "Five of the ducklings were small and yellow, but the last duckling was big and grey.",
            "emoji": "🐥",
            "highlight": "but",
            "keywords": "Five small yellow, last big grey",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p1_2",
            "text": "'He doesn't look like us! What an ugly duckling!' the other ducklings said.",
            "emoji": "🗣️",
            "keywords": "doesn't look like us, ugly duckling",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p1_3",
            "text": "'That's not nice!' said Mother Duck. 'He's still a duck like us!'",
            "emoji": "😠",
            "keywords": "not nice, still a duck",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p2",
        "text": "At the river, the ugly duckling swam well, just like all the other ducklings.",
        "emoji": "🌊",
        "highlight": "just like",
        "keywords": "swam well, just like other",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p2_1",
            "text": "But the other ducklings still laughed at him and told him to go away.",
            "emoji": "😂",
            "highlight": "But, and",
            "keywords": "laughed at, go away",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p2_2",
            "text": "It made the poor duckling very sad, so he decided to search for a new home.",
            "emoji": "😢",
            "highlight": "so",
            "keywords": "very sad, search for new home",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p2_3",
            "text": "He met many other birds, but all of them thought that he was ugly too.",
            "emoji": "🐦",
            "highlight": "but",
            "keywords": "other birds, thought ugly",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "p2_3_1",
                "text": "They did not want him to live with them.",
                "emoji": "🚫",
                "keywords": "not want him, live with",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p3",
        "text": "One day, the duckling met a cat and a hen.",
        "emoji": "🐈",
        "highlight": "One day",
        "keywords": "met cat and hen",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p3_1",
            "text": "'May I stay with you?' he asked hopefully.",
            "emoji": "🥺",
            "keywords": "stay with you",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p3_2",
            "text": "But the two animals said no.",
            "emoji": "❌",
            "highlight": "But",
            "keywords": "animals said no",
            "children": [
              {
                "id": "p3_3",
                "text": "They did not like him because he could not purr or lay eggs!",
                "emoji": "🥚",
                "highlight": "because, or",
                "keywords": "not purr, lay eggs",
                "children": []
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p4",
        "text": "Some days later, the ugly duckling came to a lake.",
        "emoji": "🏞️",
        "highlight": "Some days later",
        "keywords": "came to lake",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p4_1",
            "text": "There, he saw three beautiful swans with long necks and white feathers.",
            "emoji": "🦢",
            "highlight": "There, with",
            "keywords": "beautiful swans, long necks, white feathers",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p4_2",
            "text": "'I wish I looked like you!' he cried.",
            "emoji": "😭",
            "keywords": "wish looked like you",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p4_3",
            "text": "'My friend, you do look like us! Look in the water!' one of the swans said.",
            "emoji": "💬",
            "keywords": "look like us, Look in water",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p4_4",
            "text": "The duckling looked down, and to his surprise, he saw that he was a beautiful white swan too!",
            "emoji": "😲",
            "highlight": "and to his surprise",
            "keywords": "looked down, beautiful white swan",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
